This proxy statement (the �Proxy Statement�) solicits proxies to be voted at a special meeting (the �Meeting�) of shareholders of Savos Investments Trust (the �Trust�) to be held at the principal executive offices of the Trust at 1655 Grant Street, 10th Floor, Concord, CA 94520, on Tuesday, June 30, 2015 at 10:00 a.m., Pacific time.
