�




Proposal


Who votes on the Proposal?



To elect a Board of Trustees.��The nominees for election to the Board, all of which are currently members of the Boards of GPS Funds I and GPS Funds II (the �GPS Board�), the other funds in the AssetMark, Inc. (�AssetMark�) fund family, and one of which, Ms. Hansen, who is also currently a member of the Board of the Trust are:
